1
00:00:14,983 --> 00:00:16,108
[PRIEST 18A]
This is it.

2
00:00:16,192 --> 00:00:18,108
The time is upon us.

3
00:00:20,150 --> 00:00:24,067
At long last, our deepest desire
shall finally be fulfilled.

4
00:00:37,233 --> 00:00:39,358
Thank you so much
for the ride, Fitoria.

5
00:00:39,442 --> 00:00:41,358
We appreciate it.

6
00:00:41,442 --> 00:00:44,358
And thanks for the new
wagon you gave us, as well.

7
00:00:44,442 --> 00:00:47,692
[RAPHTALIA] Yeah. Filo really
seems to enjoy pulling them.

8
00:00:50,442 --> 00:00:51,400
[RAPHTALIA]
Hm?

9
00:00:54,067 --> 00:00:56,317
Uh--huh?

10
00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:58,858
No take-backs.
It's all mine, okay?

11
00:01:00,525 --> 00:01:02,233
She gave it to all of us, Filo.

12
00:01:02,317 --> 00:01:04,108
[RAPHTALIA, MELTY chuckle]

13
00:01:04,192 --> 00:01:05,775
Hey, Fitoria.

14
00:01:05,858 --> 00:01:08,317
Is there another hero close by?

15
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:11,358
[FITORIA]
Mm. Very close, in fact.

16
00:01:11,442 --> 00:01:13,108
Great, thanks.

17
00:01:13,192 --> 00:01:14,483
[FITORIA]
Shield Hero.

18
00:01:15,733 --> 00:01:17,692
[FITORIA]
Please take good care of her.

19
00:01:18,733 --> 00:01:21,900
[FITORIA] And don't forget--
you made me a promise.

20
00:01:23,442 --> 00:01:25,858
[NAOFUMI]
I know. I'll do what I can.

21
