<i>All the time is nearing</i>
<i>future's bleeding</i>

29
00:02:07,108 --> 00:02:10,817
<i>But I want to be</i>
<i>honest with myself</i>

30
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:12,775
<i>Come clean Follow the wind (ah?)</i>

31
00:02:12,858 --> 00:02:13,942
<i>I'm gonna make a scene</i>

32
00:02:14,025 --> 00:02:15,817
<i>Keep it real, make a mark (ah?)</i>

33
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:16,983
<i>on the masterpiece</i>

34
00:02:17,067 --> 00:02:18,442
<i>Everybody betray me</i>

35
00:02:18,525 --> 00:02:20,067
<i>Touch of your hand</i>
<i>brushed me softly</i>

36
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,400
<i>Everything betray me</i>

37
00:02:21,483 --> 00:02:23,692
<i>Shake all you want</i>
<i>But this feeling won't die</i>

38
00:02:23,775 --> 00:02:26,483
<i>Through hundreds of times</i>
<i>through millions of times</i>

39
00:02:26,567 --> 00:02:29,817
<i>I'm adding up scars</i>
<i>never giving up my faith</i>

40
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:33,150
<i>It' s proof I'm alive now,</i>
<i>always be myself</i>

41
00:02:33,233 --> 00:02:35,733
<i>I gotta make a change</i>
<i>(make a change yeah)</i>

42
00:02:35,817 --> 00:02:39,150
<i>In this distorted world</i>
<i>I follow the footsteps</i>

43
